<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Dubai Honeymoon</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">
</head>
<body>

  <!-- Hero Banner -->
  <section class="country-hero-honey" style="background: url('/img/pexels-thelazyartist-1572213.jpg');">
    <h1>Dubai Honeymoon</h1>
    <p>Luxury, adventure, and romance in one unforgettable destination</p>
  </section>

  <!-- Description -->
  <section class="country-description-honey">
    <p>
        Discover the magic of Dubai where timeless desert landscapes meet futuristic luxury. Whether you're strolling hand-in-hand through vibrant souks, enjoying a private dinner atop the world's tallest building, or relaxing in a world-class beachfront resort, Dubai offers a perfect balance of romance, adventure, and indulgence. It is the ideal destination to begin your forever together.
    </p>
  </section>

  <!-- Top Visiting Places in Dubai -->
<section class="attractions-honey">
    <h2>Most Popular Honeymoon Places in Dubai</h2>
    <div class="attraction-grid-honey">
  
      <div class="attraction-card-honey">
        <img src="/img/3f632f265c55fd526d94a1d65a54a74b.jpg" alt="Burj Khalifa">
        <h3>Burj Khalifa</h3>
        <p>Visit the world’s tallest building. Sunset from the top offers breathtaking romantic views of Dubai’s skyline.</p>
      </div>
  
      <div class="attraction-card-honey">
        <img src="/img/bd84c3b55bd92ffee2695852b0136d93.jpg" alt="Desert Safari">
        <h3>Desert Safari</h3>
        <p>Experience thrilling dune rides, camel trekking, and a private dinner under the stars in the Arabian desert.</p>
      </div>
  
      <div class="attraction-card-honey">
        <img src="/img/eb9528a0572332822a6d5a03bf1d9a2d.jpg" alt="Dubai Marina">
        <h3>Dubai Marina</h3>
        <p>Enjoy romantic waterfront walks, luxury dining, and scenic boat rides along the shimmering Marina skyline.</p>
      </div>
  
      <div class="attraction-card-honey">
        <img src="/img/b1bfa2fb5dba67db85ed2fffbe6fb2c5.jpg" alt="Palm Jumeirah">
        <h3>Palm Jumeirah</h3>
        <p>Explore this iconic island with stunning resorts, private beaches, and elegant restaurants perfect for couples.</p>
      </div>
  
      <div class="attraction-card-honey">
        <img src="/img/179ac649bd0ac4c9cfa66551bcbad580.jpg" alt="Dubai Fountain">
        <h3>Dubai Fountain</h3>
        <p>Watch the world's largest choreographed fountain show beside the Burj Khalifa — a magical moment after sunset.</p>
      </div>
  
      <div class="attraction-card-honey">
        <img src="/img/5e31b5379aa1e7d6356746f459e1f0b3.jpg" alt="Miracle Garden">
        <h3>Miracle Garden</h3>
        <p>Wander through millions of blooming flowers, heart-shaped arches, and vibrant walkways — perfect for photos together.</p>
      </div>
  
      <div class="attraction-card-honey">
        <img src="/img/d24303c957954f8993d621eaa183ee27.jpg" alt="Ain Dubai">
        <h3>Ain Dubai</h3>
        <p>Ride the world’s tallest observation wheel and take in unforgettable views of the Palm and city lights.</p>
      </div>
  
      <div class="attraction-card-honey">
        <img src="/img/02b828280bcc11ee1b25c37ad9310ab6.jpg" alt="Dubai Frame">
        <h3>Dubai Frame</h3>
        <p>Stand between the past and future of Dubai with panoramic views and a thrilling glass floor experience.</p>
      </div>
  
      <div class="attraction-card-honey">
        <img src="/img/e16437c4abd2ec2e7610751480241cbb.jpg" alt="Dubai Creek">
        <h3>Dubai Creek</h3>
        <p>Take a traditional abra boat ride through this historic waterway that showcases the city’s trading past and cultural roots.</p>
      </div>
  
    </div>
  </section>

<!-- Recommended Hotels in Dubai -->
<section class="hotels-honey">
    <h2>Romantic Stays in Dubai</h2>
    <div class="hotel-grid-honey">
  
      <div class="hotel-card-honey">
        <img src="/img/5d746acea7798b8627915f388e88ba5c.jpg" alt="Atlantis The Palm">
        <h3>Atlantis The Palm</h3>
        <p>A luxury resort on Palm Jumeirah featuring underwater suites, private beaches, and thrilling waterparks. Perfect for fun and romance.</p>
        <a href="https://www.atlantis.com/dubai/atlantis-the-palm" target="_blank">View Hotel</a>
      </div>
  
      <div class="hotel-card-honey">
        <img src="/img/02adb2943c4b3e6a7cda4cf9e707e1c6.jpg" alt="Burj Al Arab">
        <h3>Burj Al Arab</h3>
        <p>The world’s most iconic 7-star hotel offering private butler service, panoramic suites, and exclusive honeymoon experiences.</p>
        <a href="https://www.jumeirah.com/en/stay/dubai/burj-al-arab-jumeirah" target="_blank">View Hotel</a>
      </div>

      <div class="hotel-card-honey">
        <img src="/img/a2be779a5b77c66a63120d3dd77d083b.jpg" alt="Anantara The Palm Dubai">
        <h3>Anantara The Palm</h3>
        <p>A tranquil Thai-inspired resort with overwater villas, infinity pools, and lush gardens. Perfect for romantic privacy and luxury.</p>
        <a href="https://www.anantara.com/en/palm-dubai" target="_blank">View Hotel</a>
      </div>
  
      <div class="hotel-card-honey">
        <img src="/img/dd9cf9663e9e4d2aaa52c532c3394522.jpg" alt="Address Downtown">
        <h3>Address Downtown</h3>
        <p>Located beside Burj Khalifa and the Fountain, this modern hotel blends elegance and city views with luxury nightlife access.</p>
        <a href="https://www.addresshotels.com/en/hotels/address-downtown/" target="_blank">View Hotel</a>
      </div>
  
      <div class="hotel-card-honey">
        <img src="/img/6e9253859c50a305463a6a35e33d5001.jpg" alt="Armani Hotel Dubai">
        <h3>Armani Hotel Dubai</h3>
        <p>Designed by Giorgio Armani inside Burj Khalifa, this sleek hotel offers minimalist luxury and access to Dubai Mall.</p>
        <a href="https://www.armanihotels.com/en/hotels/armani-hotel-dubai/" target="_blank">View Hotel</a>
      </div>
  
      <div class="hotel-card-honey">
        <img src="/img/bdef4e6f598899128d361626141c7af5.jpg" alt="Jumeirah Al Naseem">
        <h3>Jumeirah Al Naseem</h3>
        <p>A fresh, ocean-facing hotel blending contemporary style with local charm. Offers beach access and the Wild Wadi Waterpark nearby.</p>
        <a href="https://www.jumeirah.com/en/stay/dubai/jumeirah-al-naseem" target="_blank">View Hotel</a>
      </div>
  
      <div class="hotel-card-honey">
        <img src="/img/c9e9cbd97edb71fc0c4f8b1d8246cb3a.jpg" alt="One&Only The Palm">
        <h3>One&Only The Palm</h3>
        <p>An exclusive beachfront escape offering private pools, garden courtyards, and Michelin-star dining for truly romantic stays.</p>
        <a href="https://www.oneandonlyresorts.com/the-palm" target="_blank">View Hotel</a>
      </div>
  
      <div class="hotel-card-honey">
        <img src="/img/2f46268c97559a107c90810803236fce.jpg" alt="Taj Dubai">
        <h3>Taj Dubai</h3>
        <p>Where Indian hospitality meets modern luxury. Near Burj Khalifa, it features rooftop views, romantic ambiance, and fine cuisine.</p>
        <a href="https://www.tajhotels.com/en-in/taj/taj-dubai/" target="_blank">View Hotel</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</body>
</html>
